\begin_inset Formula $Y|\theta\sim Bin(n,\theta)$
\end_inset

, where 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 is a known positive integer.
 Let the density of 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta$
\end_inset

 be
\begin_inset Formula 
