\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Show that 
\begin_inset Formula $X+Y$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $X/(X+Y)$
\end_inset

 are independent
\begin_inset space \hspace{}
\length 1cm
\end_inset

1.5p.
\end_layout

